{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9d2860233b","title":"关于注意粮食供应问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56e43b2a28","index":1,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":27,"articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"5e1cdeb6ee","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":24,"articleId":"9d2860233b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"8ad5465537","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"震林，即谭震林，当时任中共中央书记处书记。"},{"id":"7a4b386f2b","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中央警卫团干部队李宝森、王立勤、段明玉写的反映山东省一些地区缺粮情况严重的材料。"},{"id":"e8e886d780","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"按照毛泽东的批示，谭震林找李宝森等开了一个座谈会，并于1958年5月26日向毛泽东作了报告。本篇二就是毛泽东在谭震林的报告上写的批语。谭震林的报告中说：已遵示，找了警卫队季宝森等三同志开了一个座谈会，他们反映的问题基本上是对的。山东省每人平均口粮360斤，少数山区是200多斤，一般说是够吃的。去冬以来劳动强度增加，有一部分人不够吃，这是全国的现象。武汉粮食会议已解决了这个问题，我们回到北京又综合各地情况发了一次通报。粮食问题主要是增产赶不上口粮增加的需要，这个困难，估计三五年内即可能解决，即全国每人平均有一千斤粮食：口粮600斤，种子100斤，饲料200斤，余粮100斤。这个要求如果无特大灾害出现，连续三个跃进年就可能达到。如果打算有二年发生天灾善，则需五年达到这个要求。"},{"id":"be0e25c19b","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记。"},{"id":"91e5026854","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指正在举行的中共八届五中全会。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bf5ed4a298","type":"title","text":"关于注意粮食供应问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"8ad5465537","type":"paragraph","text":"震林同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"7a4b386f2b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请你一阅。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"e8e886d780","type":"paragraph","text":"山东有那么多的缺粮户，值得研究一下。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"be0e25c19b","type":"paragraph","text":"如你有时间，请找季宝森等三人（都是干部队队员，给我们守卫的，排长级干部）问一下情况。因我忙，无暇找他们谈。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"91e5026854","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"ebd6003534","type":"paragraph","text":"五月廿四日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"66a67e3a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"即送小平同志，即刻印发到会回各同志","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"fbddcb76cf","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食问题，请各同志注意。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"d1377e4c86","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"},{"id":"83a460fc94","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十七日上午二时","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b"}],"page":{"id":"5e3dad5e3d","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"9d2860233b","start":374,"end":375}}}},"__N_SSG":true}